6.28.21  4:38 pm   So as we all know, you put some subversive chords in your songs. But when do you put them in?

     Do you decide what chords you want to use and then write a melody around them?

     no

      Do you subconsciously think of them while writing a melody?

     and lyric (yes)

      Or do you look at the melody afterward and decide to spice it up by putting some new chords in?

      usually the melody already knows what chords it needs. small details can be adjusted, to taste
